reviewText: I'm sorry to say it, but when I first saw the comments here, I thought it was going to be a wonderful video. When I saw it myself, I found it awful. Most of the time they show only old Blue Angels' planes. I thought they  were gonna show some demonstration or something like this. Frustrating.

This is a great video/DVD to suppliment other action Blue Angels video. There is less emphasis on current flying stunts, and more on the background and history from 1946 on. If you want more current action, try something  else. BUt this will give you an appreciation for the background of these  great flyers.
